response.answer_text: none of our business until she announces it but that was my first thought when I saw her perform at the democratic convention. The corona robbed her of her tour but I think she’s getting a much better blessing now. The world needs more people with her energy and disposition.
That is her business not ours. It is not for any to know except her and the father if there is one. Maybe close family would know, but please keep such suppositions off the internet.
